00:37:52.850 --> 00:37:55.760
being that their parents may
not be able to afford it,

00:37:55.760 --> 00:38:01.970
or they don't have parents,
how would you advise

00:38:01.970 --> 00:38:06.167
would be a way to shift that
focus in the circumstance

00:38:06.167 --> 00:38:07.250
that they're in right now?

00:38:07.250 --> 00:38:09.715
How would they be able
to break out of that?

00:38:09.715 --> 00:38:11.840
DEMMA RODRIGUEZ: What's
your advice to young people

00:38:11.840 --> 00:38:13.520
here in the States who
